<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/949777-much-praise-lately-for-this-20-year-old">Much praise lately for this 20-year-old book but I&#39;m having trouble with it. Author makes valuable points but buries them in PAGES of silly &quot;straw men.&quot; Sort of hurts my feelings to be told not to watch for Big Foot. Not at all sure National Enquirer readers would read Sagan? Also not interested in mocking them, they have their own problems. So...does this get better? I&#39;m not at all worried about alien abduction.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_949777'><a id="like_count_community_question_949777" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/949777?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17349.The_Demon_Haunted_World">like</a></span>

