<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/5158155-david"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1427353655i/5158155._UX100_CR0,11,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/5158155-david">David</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He neither mocks nor sets up straw men. He responds to real criticisms with logical answers. He never said not to look for Big Foot. This isn&apos;t a book<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He neither mocks nor sets up straw men. He responds to real criticisms with logical answers. He never said not to look for Big Foot. This isn't a book to bring your feelings of attachment to unsubstantiated claims. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
