          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook " href="/book/show/35267489-the-demon-haunted-world">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68030-jenny-reading-envy?shelf=read2018">read2018</a>, 
